-- Euro Weakens Against U.S. Dollar and Yen, Declines 0.3 Percent to $1.3127
-- B y   N i c h o l a s   R e y n o l d s
-- 2012-02-02T09:07:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-02/euro-weakens-against-u-s-dollar-and-yen-declines-0-3-percent-to-1-3127.html
     Feb. 2 (Bloomberg) --The euro weakened against the dollar
and the yen.  The 17-nation currency declined 0.3 percent to $1.3127 at
9:05 a.m. in  London . The currency dropped 0.4 percent to 99.90
yen.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
